x27;,sans-serif] font-semibold text-[20px] text-white m-0 mb-2">Deploy</h3><p class="font-[&#x27;Roboto&#x27;,sans-serif] text-[15px] text-white/60 m-0">Launch instances in seconds. Scale up or down programmatically.</p></div></div><div class="flex justify-center mt-10"><a href="https://cloud.vast.ai/" class="no-underline"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 16px;background:#315fff;border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:8px;font-family:&#x27;Roboto&#x27;, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;line-height:16px;color:#ffffff;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;white-space:nowrap">Get Started for $5<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></a></div></div></section><section class="py-[60px] md:py-[80px]"><div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-[16px] md:px-[40px] lg:px-[40px] 2xl:px-0"><div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-lg px-[24px] md:px-[48px] lg:px-[64px] py-[48px] md:py-[64px]"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-[40px] md:gap-[48px] items-start"><div class="flex flex-col gap-6"><div><h2 class="font-[&#x27;Roboto&#x27;,sans-serif] font-bold text-[28px] md:text-[36px] text-white m-0 mb-3 leading-tight">Compare. Launch. Exit. Repeat.</h2><p class="font-[&#x27;Roboto&#x27;,sans-serif] text-[15px] md:text-[16px] text-[#b0b0b0] m-0 leading-relaxed">Every GPU on Vast.ai is provisioned through code. The same API that developers use to deploy in seconds is the interface agents use to procure and optimize at scale.</p></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-2"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="font-[&#x27;Roboto&#x27;,sans-serif] font-semibold text-[14px] text-white tracking-wide uppercase">Python SDK &amp; CLI</span></div><code c